room_title: Escape room "Nightmare on Front Street" by The Exit Games in Wilmington
room_description: You open your eyes, slowing waking as you try to remember when you even fell asleep. As you come to, panic sets in. You desperately try to find anyone or anything that you're familiar with, but all you find is darkness. You've been captured by a sick, twisted, foul being that can hardly be described as human. But why?! Why you? That's what you'll soon found out. As reality sets in, you begin to realize, you've been trapped in your own worst nightmare.....
